{"tid":2203842,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"依家局勢,留低香港好定離開好?","createTime":"2020-09-15T15:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T14:46:35.000Z","uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e4708aae05cf48c6fc9367e080a490fc7bb10696","tid":2203842,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:12:43.000Z","msg":"經歷過咁多抗爭,相信大家對香港有歸屬感,香港是我家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係到而家,又同時諗下應唔應該移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,因為見到好多人都計劃移民!<br />\n但係又唔想放棄香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔移民又好似有機會全部被共匪殲滅香港人,<br />\n走起碼防止香港人種族滅絕!<br />\n<br />\n但係同時又唔代表冇機會成功,因為香港未係最差嘅時候!雖然依家都差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!因為見到國際支持香港,所以唔代表一定失敗!<br />\n<br />\n我又睇過下歷史作為參考, 呢啲例子係反抗獨裁政權例子!<br />\n抗爭失敗例子:南越共和國<br />\n抗爭成功例子:芬蘭<br />\n仲有如果當年上個世紀,烏干達,如果印度人冇走,可能會被Edi Amin殺!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲人又希望移民,<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p5QCdtL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp5QCdtL.png&h=3b1fd943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NoFFVHs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNoFFVHs.png&h=99be1103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外,我主張生多啲,喺防止香港人滅絕,又叫我外國生!<br />\n<br />\n但有啲人要我留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gk1qnnD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgk1qnnD.png&h=6e71a968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但香港又有機會發生新疆事件,香港人被絕育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<br />\n所以有諗過走!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,點抉擇好?"},{"pid":"c563dd12605d9c2534cf90173e2704aba7379baf","tid":2203842,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"能夠走好走，好鍾意香港，但真係接受唔到，除非無能力，有能力都係走比較好，民主自由好緊要"},{"pid":"b318930e7e74dbbf13226a309de51e6727e02d56","tid":2203842,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6f28164136963e1396c1bd5fc0023cd73c2a698d","tid":2203842,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:43:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1f5a4f3a7445d9bcfc784144a10a4353f5541bf1","tid":2203842,"uid":81424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"申生在內而亡<br />\n重耳在外而安"},{"pid":"5a019730e0005324b04936d099be802aa8ce42f8","tid":2203842,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:07:38.000Z","msg":"有能力就走<br />\n走，個世界無話欠邊個<br />\n留，亦都不用羨慕妒忌，盡做啦"},{"pid":"a21cc6e925013328a00a7d73f7b6a0de68022cb8","tid":2203842,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:49:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"15a607f9229aebb3a6f2459f58a5e1017e77cc0a","tid":2203842,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"923f2f4a8044b77492e9d43a2063e62b931caefc","tid":2203842,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fe8c09f2dfa1bc73b468589587dbc94f90dadb93","tid":2203842,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:56:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3afa9181c9402919ed35f96940ac3b93b1fdad72","tid":2203842,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:56:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"adb0f39e88c7da55b9d216e5955bdf52b26835e5","tid":2203842,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T13:00:26.000Z","msg":"有條件有能力先走<br />\n留有用之軀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf301ef2d4ec6112cb7ca6e